projects.title: Game of Life
projects.body: Modeled after Conway's Game of Life simulation, this code writtin in Python demonstrates evolution scaled to thousands of generations while factoring in growth, consumption, and over-expansion in the form of dots representing individuals. The complexity of these interactions are modeled after three simple rules
